{
  "chapter": 28,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十八回 高僧的赌约\n\n小方来到西藏宫殿，面见噶伦喇嘛。噶伦喇嘛质问小方是否杀了普松，小方坦然承认。噶伦喇嘛揭示普松的真实意图——借他之手为普松复仇。噶伦喇嘛让小方取下墙上的古剑\"赤松\"，此剑乃春秋战国赤松子佩剑，十九年未饮人血，光芒已由红转碧绿。\n\n噶伦喇嘛提出赌约：小方若能杀他便可离去，否则死在他手中。小方出剑刺向噶伦喇嘛心脏，却被其以神秘武功移开心脏九寸避开，随即弹指震飞长剑。噶伦喇嘛展现返璞归真的绝世武功，令小方心服口服。\n\n噶伦喇嘛道破小方来意——他并非来看波娃，而是来杀她的，因为他身上带有杀气。噶伦喇嘛提出真正的赌约：用赤松剑杀死波娃，小方才能生存，普松之死才有代价。这是高僧的苦心，也是生死赌局。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我只问你，是不是你杀了他的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "text": "是。我不能不杀他，当时我根本没有选择的余地，他不死，我就要死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我相信你，我看得出你是个诚实的人。你还年轻，你当然不想死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "所以你也不该来的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你知不知道普松为什么要你来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "text": "他要我来见波娃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你错了。因为你不知道我们的教义和中土不同，我们不戒杀生，因为不杀生就不能降魔，我们对付妖魔、罪人、叛徒、仇敌的方法只有一种，同样的一种。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "text": "哪一种？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "以眼还眼，以牙还牙。我们相信这是惟一有效的方法，自古以来就只有这一种。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "所以现在你应该已明白，普松要你来，因为他知道我一定会杀你，替他复仇的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你信不信我在举手间就能杀了你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "墙上有剑，你不妨解下来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你为什么不拔出来看看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "text": "好剑！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这的确是柄好剑。你能杀普松，练剑至少已有十年，应该能看出这是什么剑？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "text": "这是不是春秋战国时第一高人赤松子的佩剑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是的，这柄剑就是赤松。虽然没有列入当世七柄名剑中，但那只因为世人多半以为它已被沉埋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "text": "可是故老相传，赤松的光芒本该红如夕阳，现在为什么是碧绿色的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为它有十九年未饮人血。杀人无算的利器神兵，若是多年未饮人血，不但光芒会变色，而且会渐渐失去它的锋利，甚至会渐渐变为凡铁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "text": "现在它是不是已经到了要饮血的时候？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "text": "饮谁的血？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我的血。佛祖能舍身喂鹰，为了这种神兵利器，我为何不能舍弃这副臭皮囊？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "text": "你要我用这柄剑杀了你？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "text": "你本来要杀我的。现在为什么要我杀你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我已是个老人，久已将生死看得很淡，我若杀了你，绝不会为你悲伤，你若杀了我，我也不会怪你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "所以我不妨杀了你，你也不妨杀了我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "text": "你的意思是不是说，我能杀你，就不妨杀了你，不能杀你，就得死在你手里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "良机一失，永不再来，再想回头，就已万劫不复了。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在你是不是已经相信我在举手间就能杀了你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "text": "你为什么不杀我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为我已经知道你的来意。你不是来看那个女人的，你是来杀她的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "text": "你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为你有杀气。只有决心要杀人的人，才有这种杀气，你自己虽然看不见，可是你一走入此门，我就已感觉到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我不杀你，只因为我要你去杀了她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "只有她死，你才能生，只有她死，普松的死才有代价。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "拔下这柄剑，用这柄剑去杀了她！用那魔女的血来饮饱此剑！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你一定要切切牢记，这次良机再失，就真的要永沦苦狱，万劫不复了！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    }
  ],
